  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assess the seroprevalence of neutralizing antibodies (NAb) to AAV in adults with severe
      hemophilia A (coagulation factor VIII [FVIII] &lt;1%) or moderately severe to severe hemophilia
      B (coagulation factor IX [FIX] ≤2%).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
